weighted average of the premium between perpetual and spot prices over the 8-hour interval. The exchange applies funding at 00:00, 08:00, and 16:00 UTC, with rates typically ranging from -0.375% to +0.375% daily. Portfolio margin users can leverage cross-collateral positions to optimize funding collection while maintaining delta-neutral exposure across multiple instruments."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
